(ENG)
It is very recommended not to disable the following modifications: multi lang colorful traits. HMC can work without its well, but some red errors can appears.
this mod do:
- add new weapons and ammo (EMP-ammo included too!);
- add a new traits (some of them may be dangerous!);
- add new Sharknado (why? because I can.);
- add ammo-unmaking (the game won't get any easier!);
- add new high-tech norbal and evilous drug-cat factions (be ready!);
- and more...
P.S. This modification can cause a some butthurt, feelings of hatred, anger, or severe depression.
It is strongly not recommended for particularly nervous or impressionable persons. Persons who do not accept gaming inequality in any of its manifestations, as well as for childrens, pregnant persons and retirees.

Some weapon, ammo and armour textures was taken from other mods (Gun Nut, Project Itzal, [SY4] Vanilla-Friendly Weapon Pack, dianne's defaults - Weapons, Combat Extended Guns Retextured, Eccentric Tech - Foxy's Armory, Girls' frontline Weapon Pack, EVA Core, Not Only just a cannon and other old mods whose names I don't remember anymore unfortunately) and belong to their creators, some was taken from other games, some was made by me.

